-- my-ds.page: `fastn serve`


`fastn serve [<port>]` creates an `http` server, which dynamically builds ftd files when serving.

-- ds.h1: Usage

- `fastn serve`, It will create and run server at default port `8000`
- `fastn serve 8080`, It will create and run server at port `8080`

